nodes.text: Retep V was a planet within the Mid Rim.

Above that planet, Imperial Corellian Corvettes Thrasher attempted to destroy a Habassan convoy of BFF-1 bulk freighters. The Rebel Alliance was concerned and Keyan Farlander attempted to save about half of the Starlifter freighters. After that, the Habassa tended towards the Rebellion and finally joined it.
